Interface Search<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the data type of the identifier (e.g., Integer, String)
All Known Implementing Classes:
Applicant, Application, BTO, Enquiries, Manager, Officer, Users
public interface Search<T>
Search Generic interface for enabling search operations in BTO system entities. Defines default and abstract methods for identifying items by ID, BTO project, or user association. Used for classes like BTO, Application, Users, and Enquiries to support dynamic filtering and lookup.
